#. (itstool) path: description/p
#: org.kde.kdf.appdata.xml:12
msgid ""
"KDiskFree displays the available file devices (hard drive partitions, floppy "
"and CD drives, etc.) along with information on their capacity, free space, "
"type and mount point. It also allows you to mount and unmount drives and "
"view them in a file manager."
msgstr ""
"KDiskFree prikazuje razpoložljive enote hrambe datotek (particije trdega "
"diska, diskete in pogone CD-jev itd.), skupaj s podatki o njihovi "
"kapaciteti, prostem prostoru, vrsti in mestu priključitve. Omogoča vam tudi, "
"da lahko pogone priklopite in odklopite ter si jih ogledate v upravitelju "
"datotek."

